episodes.title: Victim Impact Statement from "The Untouchable Jessica Joan. The Downfall of NXIVM" Book Launch
episodes.description:
Jessica Joan shares her Victim Impact Statement publicly for the first time at her Book Launch Party for the release of her new book "The Untouchable Jessica Joan. The Downfall of NXIVM"

Book Available on Amazon: https://a.co/d/g6pwJ89

MC: Sean Hill
